'''米瑞安·玛格莱斯'''（{{lang-en|'''Miriam Margolyes'''}}，[[大英帝國勳章|OBE]]，{{IPAc-en|ˈ|m|ɑr|ɡ|əl|iː|z}}，{{bd|1941年|5月18日|catIdx=M}}<ref name="dailymail1">{{cite news | url=http://www.dailymail.co.uk/tvshowbiz/article-1063629/My-lesbian-confession-led-mothers-stroke-says-Harry-Potter-star-Miriam-Margolyes.html | location=London | work=Daily Mail | first=James | last=Tozer | title=My lesbian confession led to mother's stroke says Harry Potter star Miriam Margolyes | date=2008-09-28 | accessdate=2013-08-08 | archive-date=2021-03-01 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210301114013/https://www.dailymail.co.uk/tvshowbiz/article-1063629/My-lesbian-confession-led-mothers-stroke-says-Harry-Potter-star-Miriam-Margolyes.html | dead-url=no }}</ref>）是一位英国出生的[[演员|演员]]和[[配音員|配音員]]。她曾因《[[纯真年代_(电影)|纯真年代]]》（1993年）中的表演获得[[英国电影学院奖|英国电影学院奖]]，还曾在《[[哈利·波特|哈利·波特]]》系列电影中扮演斯普劳特教授。

==早年生活==
玛格莱斯出生于英格兰[[牛津|牛津]]，母亲是物业投资者和开发商，父亲是来自格拉斯哥的医生。<ref name="dailymail1"/><ref>[http://www.filmreference.com/film/1/Miriam-Margolyes.html Miriam Margolyes Biography (1941–)] {{Wayback|url=http://www.filmreference.com/film/1/Miriam-Margolyes.html |date=20210227003105 }}. Filmreference.com. Retrieved 25 August 2011.</ref>她在一个[[犹太人|犹太]]家庭长大。<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.dailyrecord.co.uk/showbiz/celebrity-news/2011/11/02/exclusive-miriam-margolyes-attacks-john-cleese-and-other-python-stars-in-exclusive-interview-86908-23532309/ |title=Harry Potter actress Miriam Margolyes on her Gorbals roots, women in comedy and how Monty Python stars shunned her |publisher=The Daily Record |date=2011-11-02 |accessdate=2011-12-21 |archive-date=2012-07-04 |archive-url=https://www.webcitation.org/68uuWydSS?url=http://www.dailyrecord.co.uk/showbiz/celebrity-news/2011/11/02/exclusive-miriam-margolyes-attacks-john-cleese-and-other-python-stars-in-exclusive-interview-86908-23532309/ |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite news | url=http://www.telegraph.co.uk/comment/6291521/Miriam-Margolyes-Im-still-a-naughty-schoolgirl-at-heart.html | location=London | work=The Daily Telegraph | first=Nigel | last=Farndale | title=Miriam Margolyes: 'I'm still a naughty schoolgirl at heart' | date=2009-10-11 | accessdate=2013-08-08 | archive-date=2021-03-09 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210309062221/https://www.telegraph.co.uk/comment/6291521/Miriam-Margolyes-Im-still-a-naughty-schoolgirl-at-heart.html | dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>http://www.scotsman.com/lifestyle/edinburgh-festivals/all-articles/as-miriam-margolyes-prepares-to-perform-her-one-woman-show-dedicated-to-the-women-in-the-victorian-novelist-s-fiction-she-reflects-on-her-own-fascinating-life-story-1-2452037</ref>她的父母都是来自[[白俄罗斯|白俄罗斯]]的移民后裔。她毕业于当地的牛津高中<ref name="dailymail1"/>，然后来到[[剑桥大学|剑桥大学]][[剑桥大学纽纳姆学院|纽纳姆学院]]学习英语。<ref>[http://www.newn.cam.ac.uk/joining-newnham/undergraduate-admissions/subjects/content/english Newnham College undergraduate admissions page for English] {{webarchive|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130818195813/http://www.newn.cam.ac.uk/joining-newnham/undergraduate-admissions/subjects/content/english |date=2013-08-18 }}. Newn.cam.ac.uk. Retrieved 25 August 2011.</ref>在那里，20多岁的她开始演戏。<ref>[http://footlights.org/alumni.html Footlights Alumni] {{webarchive|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110814004206/http://footlights.org/alumni.html |date=2011-08-14 }}. Footlights.org. Retrieved 25 August 2011.</ref>

==个人生活==
玛格莱斯是公开的[[同性恋|同性恋]]<ref>[[The_Graham_Norton_Show|The Graham Norton Show]], 4 March 2011</ref>，和她的伴侣Heather<ref name="southernhighlandnews1">{{cite web |author=Leah O'Brien |url=http://www.southernhighlandnews.com.au/news/local/news/entertainment/at-home-with-harry-potter-star-miriam-margolyes/1826576.aspx |title=At home with Harry Potter star, Miriam Margolyes - Local News - News - Entertainment |publisher=Southern Highland News |date=2010-05-11 |accessdate=2011-12-21 |archive-date=2012-04-07 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120407131035/http://www.southernhighlandnews.com.au/news/local/news/entertainment/at-home-with-harry-potter-star-miriam-margolyes/1826576.aspx |dead-url=no }}</ref>一起生活超过40年。<ref name="dailymail1"/>在2013年的[[澳大利亞日|澳大利亞日]]她正式成为澳大利亚公民。<ref name=latenightlive>[http://www.abc.net.au/rn/latenightlive/stories/2007/2028953.htm Late Night Live – 10September2007 – Miriam Margolyes and Dickens' Women] {{Wayback|url=http://www.abc.net.au/rn/latenightlive/stories/2007/2028953.htm |date=20090725141923 }}. Abc.net.au (10 September 2007). Retrieved 25 August 2011.</ref>

玛格莱斯是一个[[巴勒斯坦|巴勒斯坦]]人权活动家，旨在结束以色列对加沙地带和约旦河西岸的占领。<ref>[http://electronicintifada.net/v2/article6451.shtml "Emma Thompson bids for Palestinian Rights Enough!"] {{Wayback|url=http://electronicintifada.net/v2/article6451.shtml |date=20101009033531 }} 27 January 2007, Electronic Intifada</ref>

